@Node Introduction "Introduction"

Having started using the excellent AmiBroker, I found myself  continually 
looking up share prices and manually entering them into this fine program.
This soon becomes a pain if you are trying to keep track of any number of 
shares on a daily basis. AmiBrokers Teletext quotes system only works in 
Poland at the moment.

What is even more annoying is that all the shares I want to keep track of
are quoted daily on the Internet. So in the end I wrote these scripts to
download the prices I wanted and create an ASCII data file which can be
loaded into Amibroker.


@EndNode
